msgstr "Brązowa shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1254
msgid "Lime Shulker Box"
msgstr "Jasnozielona shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1255
msgid "Green Shulker Box"
msgstr "Zielona shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1256
msgid "Pink Shulker Box"
msgstr "Różowa shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1257
msgid "Red Shulker Box"
msgstr "Czerwona shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1258
msgid "Grey Shulker Box"
msgstr "Szara shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1259
msgid "Black Shulker Box"
msgstr "Czarna shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1285 mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1356
msgid "Shulker Box"
msgstr "Shulkerowa skrzynia"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1314 mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1509
msgid "Can be carried around with its contents"
msgstr "Może być przenoszona razem z zawartością"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1337
msgid "and @1 more"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1353
msgid ""
"A shulker box is a portable container which provides 27 inventory slots for "
"any item except shulker boxes. Shulker boxes keep their inventory when "
"broken, so shulker boxes as well as their contents can be taken as a single "
"item. Shulker boxes come in many different colors."
msgstr ""
"Shulkerowe skrzynie to przenośny pojemnik udostępniający 27 miejsc ekwipunku "
"na dowolny przedmiot z wyjątkiem shulkerowych skrzyń. Shulkerowe skrzynie "
"nie tracą swojego ekwipunku po zniszczeniu, więc te skrzynie razem z całą "
"zawartością mogą być przechowywane jako pojedynczy przedmiot."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_chests/init.lua:1355
msgid ""
"To access the inventory of a shulker box, place and right-click it. To take "
"a shulker box and its contents with you, just break and collect it, the "
"items will not fall out. Place the shulker box again to be able to retrieve "
"its contents."
msgstr ""
